Prior to tagging, do the following:

- change the version of the code in the 'svn export' section of doc/source/index.rst

- change the version in doc/source/conf.py

- 'make html' the documentation

- svn ci all of that

- tag using, e.g., svn copy svn+ssh://sdss3svn@sdss3.org/repo/xdqso/trunk svn+ssh://sdss3svn@sdss3.org/repo/xdqso/tags/v0_7 -m "xdqso: tagging v0_7"
